reviews.text: I love Toast Box but this branch was quite terrible. Terrible laksa as it felt like it was missing an important ingredient - didn't even taste like laksa actually. Almost nowhere to sit as most of the tables are unclean.
Simple good meal for a descent price

I can’t express my emotions about this place , toast box is one of the most amazing places that I truly enjoy their tea , toast , the ones in Hk are just run by extremely rude staff , not one single word in English , no understanding what so ever , I can’t imagine how the management let them get away by serving such a bad service , a nightmare if you are unable to communicate with them in Cantonese and be rude about it , they get every order wrong even though I know the original names of each tea in the original Chinese names , 
Ahhhhh some higher management should look at the these comments
Great coffee as always. And they're the closest in Hong Kong to an authentic Singaporean cafe
Toast with kaya and butter is to die for. The tea is excellent!!

reviews.text: I love Toast Box but this branch was quite terrible. Terrible laksa as it felt like it was missing an important ingredient - didn't even taste like laksa actually. Almost nowhere to sit as most of the tables are unclean.
咖㖿多士好好味，但公仔麵就麻麻地
食物漸縮水，咖哩雞飯由大大塊雞球有雞胸有雞脾，變成細雞翼，太令人失望，本來真的好好吃的－個飯就此摧毀了｡另外遺－可取的奶茶，質數不穩定，次次喝會不同味，其他分店也有明顯味道分別，看運數吧~另外這店買很多餐都－定跟煎雙蛋，改别的不許，令人苦惱着急
Simple good meal for a descent price
